8jJbgRNg">Thường Kiến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-m8buZGd9acbui1906QmgWA">Thanh Tâm tài nhân tập tự - 青心才人詩集序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/author-ZpBj6D9P3q-U3JR36g_w5g">Chu Mạnh Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Giang/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-o86xUkD6XWLqGPfWGwnNoA">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Giang/author-8p_fx7jeERd4MvdKnNv_Wg">Tống Giang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-V%E1%BA%A1n-l%C3%BD-phong-ba-nh%E1%BA%A5t-di%E1%BB%87p-chu/poem-_Yzejx-ikiqoz8pJ3Zh9-g">Vô đề (Vạn lý phong ba nhất diệp chu) - 無題（萬里風波一葉舟）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
